OL,3,CBradley Lowery's dad severely burnt in
OL,4,Cworkplace accident
OL,6,FThe dad of Bradley Lowery underwent
OL,7,Fmultiple surgeries and a skin graft
OL,8,Fafter being severely burnt while at
OL,9,Fwork - just three years after the
OL,10,Fyoungster's death.
OL,12,FCarl Lowery, had been working on new
OL,13,Fapartment blocks in Salford, Greater
OL,14,FManchester when an electrical flash
OL,15,Fblew him backwards and burnt his arms
OL,16,Fand face on 12 May 2020.
OL,18,FThe then 37-year-old underwent
OL,19,Fmultiple surgeries following the
OL,20,Fincident and required a skin graft
OL,21,Ffrom his thigh.
