OL,3,CBradley Lowery's dad severely burnt in
OL,4,Cworkplace accident
OL,6,FThe incident happened almost three
OL,7,Fyears after Carl lost six-year-old son
OL,8,Fto a rare form of cancer.
OL,10,FThe fan captured the hearts of the
OL,11,Fnation during his battle with
OL,12,Fneuroblastoma, appearing as a mascot
OL,13,Ffor Sunderland and England alongside
OL,14,F"best friend" Defoe, before dying in
OL,15,F2017.
OL,17,FAlong with his wife Gemma, Carl
OL,18,Festablished the Bradley Lowery
OL,19,FFoundation, which helps families that
OL,20,Fare fundraising to obtain medical
OL,21,Fequipment and treatment.
