OL,3,CBradley Lowery's dad severely burnt in
OL,4,Cworkplace accident
OL,6,FThe dad has not been able to work
OL,7,Fsince the incident, and forced to
OL,8,Flearn to use his non-dominant hand to
OL,9,Fcarry out tasks.
OL,11,FIn a victim personal statement, given
OL,12,Fto a court following an investigation
OL,13,Fby the Health and Safety Executive
OL,14,F(HSE), he said: "Even when Bradley was
OL,15,Fpoorly I worked. I've not been able to
OL,16,Fwork since the accident either,
OL,17,Fmentally or physically.
