OL,3,CBradley Lowery's dad severely burnt in
OL,4,Cworkplace accident
OL,6,F"My left hand is my dominant hand and
OL,7,Fafter the accident I had no grip. I
OL,8,Fhad to try and learn how to use my non-
OL,9,Fdominant hand."
OL,11,FAfter pleading guilty to a health and
OL,12,Fsafety offence, the company was fined
OL,13,F#40,000 and ordered to pay #20,000 in
OL,14,Fcosts at Manchester Magistrates' Court
OL,15,Fon 14 March 2024.
OL,17,FCarl, now 41, had been working
OL,18,Falongside a colleague at SRE Cabling
OL,19,Fand Jointing Limited to carry out
OL,20,Fworks on the news apartments at The
OL,21,FCrescent, Hulme Street.
