OL,3,CBradley Lowery's dad severely burnt in
OL,4,Cworkplace accident
OL,6,FThe company had been sub-contracted by
OL,7,FAberla M&E Limited.
OL,9,FThe pair were working on the
OL,10,Fbuilding's main switchboard, with
OL,11,Fnearby bus bars - a metallic strip or
OL,12,Fbar - left live with electricity and
OL,13,Fcovered by a guard panel.
OL,15,FHowever, a nut rolled behind a gap in
OL,16,Fthe guard panel and came into contact
OL,17,Fwith the live current, causing the
OL,18,Felectrical flash and blowing Carl
OL,19,Fbackwards, burning his arms and face.
