OL,3,CBradley Lowery's dad severely burnt in
OL,4,Cworkplace accident
OL,6,FThe HSE investigation into this
OL,7,Fincident found Aberla M&E Limited had
OL,8,Fincorrectly assumed the guard panel
OL,9,Fwas sufficient separation of the
OL,10,Fworkers from the live bus bars.
OL,12,FThe company failed to take into
OL,13,Faccount a gap in the guard panel,
OL,14,Fwhich risked nuts, bolts, tools and
OL,15,Feven fingers coming into contact with
OL,16,Fthe bus bars.
OL,18,FThere was also a failure to issue a
OL,19,Fpermit to work (PTW) on or near live
OL,20,Fcomponents, which resulted in the main
OL,21,Fswitchboard being left live.
