OL,3,CBradley Lowery's dad severely burnt in
OL,4,Cworkplace accident
OL,6,FThe investigation also found a
OL,7,Fdistinct lack of live works monitoring
OL,8,Fby the company, with the electrical
OL,9,Fsite manager rarely visiting the work
OL,10,Farea.
OL,12,FHSE inspector Lisa Bailey said: "This
OL,13,Fincident has had life-changing
OL,14,Fconsequences for Carl and his family.
OL,15,FIt could have been avoided if the
OL,16,Fcompany had actively monitored and
OL,17,Fmanaged procedures, to identify risks
OL,18,Fand prevent incidents.
