OL,3,CBradley Lowery's dad severely burnt in
OL,4,Cworkplace accident
OL,6,F"Working with electricity is a high-
OL,7,Frisk activity and safety must be a
OL,8,Fpriority. Proper planning to ensure
OL,9,Fthat risks are eliminated at system
OL,10,Fdesign stage is essential."
OL,12,FAberla M&E Limited, of The Parklands,
OL,13,FBolton, Greater Manchester, pleaded
OL,14,Fguilty to breaching Section 3(1) of
OL,15,Fthe Health and Safety at Work etc. Act
OL,16,F1974.
